# OrangeHRM Test Case Document

This repository contains functional test cases for the OrangeHRM demo web application:  
ðŸ‘‰ [https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com]

The test cases are documented in an Excel file and cover several key authentication features.

ðŸ“„ File Included

- `Test_Case_OrangeHRM.xlsx`  
  Contains test cases for the following components:
  - Login (positive and negative scenarios)
  - Forgot Password
  - Logout

# Test Case Columns
Each test case includes the following columns:
- TestCaseID
- Platform
- Component
- Kind of Test (Positive/Negative)
- Priority (High/Medium/Low)
- Description / Test Scenario
- Test Steps
- Test Data
- Expected Result
- Actual Result
- Status (Pass/Fail)
- Notes

âœ… How to Use
1. Open the Excel file.
2. Review each test scenario and steps.
3. Update the "Actual Result" and "Status" after executing the tests.
4. This document can be used for manual testing or as a reference for automation.

ðŸ“Œ Notes

- This is a test case document for learning purposes.
- The scenarios are based on public OrangeHRM demo system.
